creator: ITXpress A/S
descriptionHtml:
Get the free app, as part of your company's anysense ® subscription. Does your company not have anysense® yet, read more here:

The purpose of anysense®, is at once eliminating paper forms, as well as utilize the technological developments in the field of mobile and sensor technology for mobile documentation. You can take any paper form and digitize it anysense®. The fields may have special features, such as taking pictures directly on your mobile device into the field. In the same way, as an example also the GPS, microphone, and accelerometer.

Popular uses are:
1) Quality Control,
2) Building inspections,
3) Daysheets,
4) Material Management (Registration of equipment with GPS and Picture etc.) so you always know where your equipment is located.
5) Documentation

anysense ® consists primarily by a web portal where you design forms that are meant to be forms on various mobile devices such as smartphones, tablets and notebooks. In addition to the common fields can form the data fields consist of sensor fields that use the entity sensors, creating unique opportunities. For example, use the entity camera as a field consisting of images taken directly from the device and automatically stored in the field.
descriptionShort: The purpose of anysense®, is at once eliminating paper forms.
